<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693075>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–4. Cryphocricos barozzii (1) holotype, (2) brachypterous female from Rosario River, Rio Grande do Sul, Brazil, (3) abdominal terga showing dark tubercles near middle of III–V, (4) subgenital plate of two specimens from Nova Teutonia, Brazil showing intrapopulational variation in shape of posterior margin. Figure 1 courtesy of NHMW Hemiptera Image Collection / Harald Bruckner and Herbert Zettel." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693075/files/figure.png" .

